lead_paragraph: An eager Michael Phelps made his long-awaited appearance at the U.S. Olympic trials on Tuesday by posting the top time in the 200 metres butterfly heats that, for many fans, was the official start of the meet.

headline.main: Phelps Eases Into 200m Butterfly Semis at Olympic Trials
